Dear_Latin lovers ,
We ' re excited to introduce to you new dancing floor for Salsaholic in Saigon . Salsa_Tuesday night in Jan 19th will be the very first trial for you to test the wooden floor , amazing sound system for a cozy social night . Welcome you all to our first Salsa party of 2016 , as a good start of a great year ahead with many more events going to be host at ZFit . We ' ll serve a bit of finger food & mocktail for early guest , hope you come to support us as usual .
DJ_VIOH will be your man that night , bringing the best of his collection for a beautiful Salsa night in town .
A ) TICKET_ENTRANCE ( included 1 soft drink ) :
- Individual : 60,000 / person
- Group of 4 & more : 50,000 / person
B ) TIME : 20 : 30 - 23 : 30 , Tuesday , Jan 19th 2016
C ) VENUE : Basement level ( parking area ) , 02 Ho_Xuan_Huong , District 3 ( Ho_Xuan_Huong_Sport_Center )
* parking fee after 22 : 00 is 8,000
Welcome all & hope to dance with you ! ; )
